Law wey be M. Gressette Jr., president, dem appoint am to di additional post of chairman and chief executive officer for dis utility wey be company wey dey hold company, EFCC, on February 1, 1990.

Di 57 years old Oga, Gressette wey dem still elect as chairman and chief executive of all Scana subsidiary, na im dey succeed John A. Warren.

Oga Warren go remain on top di company board.

